---
import KitLayout from '../../layouts/KitLayout.astro';
---
<KitLayout title="Kit">
  <h1>Kit</h1>
  <p><strong>v2 &mdash; coming after v1 ships.</strong></p>
  <p>
    Multi-widget components that handle complex layout, multi-step state,
    or external library integration.
  </p>
  <p>
    If it can be built in under 30 lines from atoms, it belongs in
    <a href="/sigil/patterns/">Patterns</a> (docs only). Otherwise it ships here.
  </p>

  <h2>Planned molecules</h2>

  <h3 id="colorpicker">ColorPicker</h3>
  <p>
    HTML hex colors and CSS named colors. Two views via TabBar: a palette grid
    of named color cells (spatial nav across cells, each cell's background is
    the color) and a custom view with RGB sliders + hex text input.
  </p>
  <p>Composes: Panel, TabBar, Slider, TextField, Box.</p>
  <p>Props: <code>value</code>, <code>onChange</code>, <code>palette</code> (predefined hex colors for the palette tab).</p>

  <h4>Palette view</h4>
  <pre class="ascii-mockup">┌ Color ──────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                                                 │
│  <span class="focused">┌ Palette ┐</span> Custom │                           │
│  ├─────────┴────────────────────────────────┐   │
│  │                                          │   │
│  │  (grid of named color cells, each cell   │   │
│  │   is a space with bg = that color)       │   │
│  │                    ▸                     │   │
│  │                                          │   │
│  └──────────────────────────────────────────┘   │
│                                                 │
│  Selected: coral      #FF7F50   ████            │
│                                 preview         │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────┘</pre>

