│  │  └──────────────────────┘   preview      │   │
│  └──────────────────────────────────────────┘   │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────┘</pre>

  <h3 id="datepicker">DatePicker</h3>
  <p>
    Three drill-down views (day &rarr; month &rarr; year), following
    Android/iOS date picker patterns. Tapping the header label drills into the
    next view. Optional time tab with NumberInput spinners for hour and minute.
  </p>
  <p>Composes: Panel, TabBar, ListBox, NumberInput, Button, Box.</p>
  <p>Props: <code>value</code>, <code>onChange</code>, <code>min</code>, <code>max</code> (date range constraints), <code>showTime</code>.</p>

  <h4>Day view</h4>
