│ Unit             │  Pts  │  W  │
├──────────────────┼───────┼─────┤
│                                │
│         No data                │
│                                │
└──────────────────┴───────┴─────┘</pre>

  <h4>Paginated</h4>
  <pre class="ascii-mockup">│ ...                            │
├──────────────────┼───────┼─────┤
│              Page 2 of 5       │
│           ◀  1  2  3  ▶        │
└────────────────────────────────┘</pre>

  <h3 id="commandpalette">CommandPalette</h3>
  <p>
    Fuzzy-find actions. Dialog + TextField + filtered ListBox. Displays matching
    actions as the user types, with a "no matching actions" empty state.
  </p>
  <p>Composes: Dialog, TextField, ListBox, useFilter.</p>
  <p>Props: <code>actions</code>, <code>onSelect</code>, <code>onClose</code>.</p>

  <pre class="ascii-mockup"><span class="focused">┌─────────────────────────────────────┐</span>
<span class="focused">│</span> > add un█                           <span class="focused">│</span>
<span class="focused">│</span> ┌─────────────────────────────────┐ <span class="focused">│</span>
<span class="focused">│</span> │ <span class="focused">▸ Add Unit</span>                      │ <span class="focused">│</span>
<span class="focused">│</span> │   Add Unit to Reserve           │ <span class="focused">│</span>
<span class="focused">│</span> │   Undo Last Action              │ <span class="focused">│</span>
<span class="focused">│</span> └─────────────────────────────────┘ <span class="focused">│</span>
<span class="focused">└─────────────────────────────────────┘</span></pre>

  <p>No results:</p>
  <pre class="ascii-mockup">┌─────────────────────────────────────┐
│ > xyzzy█                            │
│                                     │
│   No matching actions               │
│                                     │
└─────────────────────────────────────┘</pre>

  <h3 id="autocomplete">Autocomplete</h3>
  <p>
    TextField with suggestions dropdown. Popover positioned below the input.
    Dropdown only appears after typing. Supports a "no matches" empty state.
  </p>
  <p>Composes: TextField, ListBox, useFilter, Popover.</p>
  <p>Props: <code>value</code>, <code>onChange</code>, <code>options</code>, <code>onSelect</code>.</p>

  <pre class="ascii-mockup">Typing:                             No results:
<span class="focused">╭────────────────────────────────╮</span>  <span class="focused">╭────────────────────────────────╮</span>
<span class="focused">│</span>Iron Leg█                       <span class="focused">│</span>  <span class="focused">│</span>xyzzy█                          <span class="focused">│</span>
├────────────────────────────────┤  ├────────────────────────────────┤
│ <span class="focused">▸ Iron Legion</span>                  │  │  No matches                    │
│   Iron Guard                   │  └────────────────────────────────┘
│   Iron Horde                   │
└────────────────────────────────┘</pre>

  <h3 id="toast">Toast</h3>
  <p>
    Auto-dismissing notification. High-z patch, no focus trap. Timer unmounts
    it. Multiple toasts stack vertically. Not interactive (no focus).
  </p>
  <p>Composes: Box (high z), Text, timer.</p>
  <p>Props: <code>message</code>, <code>duration</code>, <code>intent</code> (info/success/warning/error).</p>

  <pre class="ascii-mockup">Single:              ┌─────────────────────────┐
                     │  Unit added to roster   │
                     └─────────────────────────┘

Stacked:             ┌─────────────────────────┐
                     │  Settings saved         │
                     └─────────────────────────┘
                     ┌─────────────────────────┐
                     │  Unit added to roster   │
                     └─────────────────────────┘</pre>

  <h3 id="popover">Popover</h3>
  <p>
    Positioning primitive. High-z Box anchored to a trigger element's grid
    bounds. Takes anchor NodeId + placement (above/below/left/right), computes
    origin from layout bounds, renders children in a high-z Box. Used by
    Autocomplete, Tooltip, and ContextMenu.
  </p>
  <p>Not a widget &mdash; a positioning utility.</p>

  <pre class="ascii-mockup">  ┌──────────┐
  │ Rename   │           ┌────────────────────────┐
  │ Delete   │           │ Tip: press Tab to move │
  │ Inspect  │           │ between fields.        │
  └──────────┘           └────────────────────────┘
   context menu               tooltip</pre>
</KitLayout>
